{"tid":1550363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「隆重登場」香港國歌英文版本","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:46:00.000Z","uid":124156,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9819e4834107e625a07e35f299b362c7bd4e24e2","tid":1550363,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kb6jXeK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkb6jXeK.png&h=04c6e6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有人幫手唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<br />\nOur tears seep through this weeping land,<br />\nOur ears hear the raging of men.<br />\nWe rise and we cry a-front our stand,<br />\nLet this land be free again!<br />\n<br />\nOur fears, though they stayed like a wraith,<br />\nThe years never stopped our rooted faith!<br />\nOur chants ring aloud along the bloodied path,<br />\nBuild this land o&rsquo;er our wrath!<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Tis the night stars fall and all seem lost,<br />\nHeed the horn, amidst the haze and through the skies!<br />\nWe gather for freedom and rights, no matter the cost,<br />\nOur strength and wisdom never dies!<br />\n<br />\nOur dawn has come, let us write the pages!<br />\nFor our home, revolution of the ages!<br />\nFor our men, by our men ere the end of time,<br />\nFor the rise of Hong Kong&rsquo;s prime!<br />\n<br />\n推到全世界都識英文 version！！！<br />\n<br />\n正評=支持"},{"pid":"ae0359874f6e0653520dae906163312592c070eb","tid":1550363,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3481a3fdd9e6920e6999b9cf876eb0611ea88244","tid":1550363,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"巴絲打們一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b3eca1dc1963335dd35a1e66e6ca2f0d47aab3","tid":1550363,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"cb993ca378e5faae0bc74b989ae36841e6021dbd","tid":1550363,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"8917392ca9ace978c8c2a440f70fe0bd47bca9c1","tid":1550363,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55350651b28245467fcadd5778c6dbca53bb0ce","tid":1550363,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ef4ff9f6693ccc43c650194af0c6e8def8be1c","tid":1550363,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-